des: A radio station supporting Kansas City Pet Project. KC Pet Project is leading the way in creating a compassionate, safe community for pets and people through progressive, lifesaving programs and services, community resources, and educational opportunities. KCPP Radio broadcasts a Greatest Hits format with music from the 80's, 90's and today. Listen, enjoy and learn more about KC Pet Project!
